title: It's HOT Outside, Come Check Out Our Cool Prices!
posting_body: ['1520 West Casino Road, Everett, WA 98204', 'The Lynx Apartments offers one-and two-bedroom apartments in Everett, Washington.', 'Our apartment community is ideally located minutes from Boeing, the Mukilteo ferries, the Port of Everett, shopping, dining and major freeways.', 'Our community resides on the Walter Hall Golf Course in Everett and every home at The Lynx Apartments offers spectacular golf course views.', 'Schedule a tour today to see why you’ll love living at The Lynx Apartments!', 'Apartment Features:', 'Wood Burning Fireplace', 'Dishwasher', 'Vaulted Ceilings in Top Floor Homes', 'Full Size Washer & Dryers', 'Extra Storage', 'Ceiling Fan', 'Community Features:', 'Courtyard', 'Seasonal Heated Outdoor Swimming Pool', 'Resident Clubhouse', 'Golf Course Views', 'Translation Service Available', 'TV Lounge with Wifi', 'Call:', 'show contact info', 'For more information, visit us at: <URL>', '*Pricing and availability are subject to change daily.', 'Photos may not be of the exact advertised unit.', 'Please contact us today for the most up to date information!']
